title: Nathan Pendleton - Hello Echo (2014) mp3
description:
Greetings from Lexington, Kentucky! Thanks for supporting independent releases.

Artist: Nathan Pendleton
Album: Hello Echo
Year: 2014
Format: 44100 Hz, 192 Kbps, mp3, stereo

1. Your Wicked Heart - Feat. Sundog Revival
2. Harlan County Blues
3. Someday I'm Coming Down - Feat. Sundog Revival
4. Good St. Anne
5. Woke Up One Morning
6. The Ballad of Captain Mallory
7. Jordan River Blues
8. Dragon Attack! - Feat. Sundog Revival
9. Mambo Sun
10. Goliath
11. One of These Things
12. Papercut - Feat. Sundog Revival

All songs written by Nathan Pendleton except "Mambo Sun" by Marc Bolan and "Dragon Attack!" by Brian May. 

All instruments performed by Nathan Pendleton except those with the Sundog Revival:

Kendra Sluss - vocals
Brandon May - bass guitar
Joe Hall - drums
Sean Cutshall - saxophone

Otherwise, this album was played, engineered, recorded, mixed, and produced by Nathan Pendleton.
